	<div id="content" class="hfeed">
	<article class="post-615825 post type-post status-publish hentry category-industrials category-mergers-acquisitions tag-alstom tag-bouygues tag-general-electric-company tag-immelt-jeffrey-r tag-kaeser-joe tag-mergers-acquisitions-and-divestitures tag-mitsubishi-heavy-industries-limited tag-siemens-ag per-immelt-jeffrey-r per-kaeser-joe des-mergers-acquisitions-and-divestitures org-alstom org-bouygues org-general-electric-company org-mitsubishi-heavy-industries-limited org-siemens-ag" id="post-615825">
	<header class="postHeader">
